gui_verbose(25.10)                                          gui_verbose(25.10)

Name
       gui_verbose

Syntax
        gui_verbose {all db none}

       Type: enum {all db none}, read/write

       Default: db

       Controls which GUI actions are logged. You can select:

              * all: Logs all GUI actions.

              * db:  Logs  the GUI actions that affect the DB, such as gui_se-
                lect, but  does  not  capture  display-only  actions  such  as
                gui_dim_foreground.

              * none:  Does  not  log  any  GUI actions. So, the .log and .cmd
                files are incomplete.

